        <message_html><![CDATA[<p><span style="color: #000000; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">Dear ${name},</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">As a manager, you are accountable for the performance of your team, which includes providing feedback, recognizing and reinforcing strong performance in your employees, identify and encourage improvement where needed. &nbsp;Over 99% of Parker employees have completed their self-assessment and are eager to hear from you.&nbsp; Please, plan to meet with your employees by February 9, to review their final ratings, goals and development for 2018.&nbsp; After the meeting &ldquo;Acknowledge&rdquo; the discussion has taken place in PDR, this will send the form back to the employee where final comments can be added to the form.&nbsp; Please, remind your employees to complete PDR by clicking the &ldquo;Acknowledge&rdquo; button. As soon they do this the status of PDR will change to &ldquo;Complete&rdquo;.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;"><code class="ph codeph">${mail_script:pending_pdrs}</code> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;"><br /> If you have questions, please, contact your local HR representative.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;"><em><br /> <span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #003366;"><strong>Talent Management Team</strong></span></em></span></p>]]></message_html>
